precis:
Enactment of the INTERPROVINCIAL MOVEMENT OF HAZARDOUS WASTE REGULATIONS
which provide that no one shall transport hazardous waste between provinces
unless the shipment is accompanied by a manifest, effective
August 15, 2002.
